Package: toxdrc
Title: toxdrc
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Jack", "Salole", , "salolej@mcmaster.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: toxdrc provides a variety of tools for assessing dose response curves, with an emphasis on toxicity test data. The main feature of this package are modular functions which combine to form pipelines to automate data analysis for large datasets. Data can also be manipulated during this pipeline (outliers, CV calculation, validity criteria, etc.)
